item.title: Sv2
item.author: thisemaildoesnotexist@www.example.com (OSPG)
item.description: Project URL: github.com/OSPG/sv2 Language: Go Summary: An utility to improve the security of a system. SV2 analyzes the current configurations of the system and provides recommendations to harden it against possible attackers.

item.title: Godedupe
item.author: thisemaildoesnotexist@www.example.com (OSPG)
item.description: Project URL: github.com/OSPG/godedupe Language: Go Summary: An utility to find duplicated files. Godedupe finds duplicated files like fdupes does. Unlike fdupes, we focus on speed and features.
